technology

Our project utilizes many different emerging technolgies. For example, we use bluetooth in conjunction with the arduino 
software serial module to send and recieve data between our laptop and the scout car. We also took advantage of the
python programming language and its powerful libraries. Using this, along with the adruino-oriented c++ libraries, we
were able to create synergistc code. Lastly we used an eyetracking device to gather gaze data, which is a set of precise
coordinates located where user is looking on his or her screen. 

The servos are remotely controlled by an algorithm we created. The algorithm takes the user's real time gaze data as input, processes it, and then
maps this input to servo angles. For example, if the user is looking at the top left region of the screen, the servos will move the laser
pointer up and to the left. All of this done simutaneously while the user is able to navigate the scout car.

conclusion:
In conclusion, this was just a simple proof of concept to demonstrate various technogolies capabilites and their applications in
defense, security, and even aerospace. There is of course a lot of potential improvements to be made to our project
in order to exapand its functionality and practicality. Thank you for this opportunity to develope useful technical skills.
